Stir together cream cheese, bacon, dates, sherry, parsley and green onion. (For crunchiest texture, stir in almonds just before serving.) Cover and refrigerate for 1 hour or up to 2 days. To serve, stir in almonds and spoon spread in small serving dish. Set dish in center of large platter and surround with Keebler(R) Toasteds(R) Crackers.